                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100">8 000 - 14 000 zł</td>
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100">10 000 - 18 000 zł</td>
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100">12 000 - 22 000 zł</td>
                   </tr>
                   <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors">
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100"><strong>Materiały instalacyjne (kanały, kształtki, anemostaty itp.)</strong></td>
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100">7 000 - 12 000 zł</td>
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100">9 000 - 15 000 zł</td>
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100">11 000 - 18 000 zł</td>
                   </tr>
                   <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-colors">
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100"><strong>Montaż i uruchomienie systemu (robocizna)</strong></td>
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100">7 000 - 10 000 zł</td>
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100">8 000 - 12 000 zł</td>
                       <td class="p-4 border-b border-zinc-100">9 000 - 15 000 zł</td>
